Brahma is the annual national level techno-cultural fest of Adi Shankara institute of Engineering and technology. 
2016 will witness the 13th edition of the fest and it will feature exciting events spread over cultural, technical, and general disciplines.


The events of Brahma aim at bringing the best out of engineering students from all over the nation. Apart from these, there will be an array of fun events, galleries, and stalls at the fest. The first day of the fest will be dedicated entirely to the classical artforms.


Prize money of nearly a million will be up for grabs in the three-day fest and we are bound to see the rise of new heroes. Be there to witness the making of history and awaken the creator within.
